* MERGE for\nSCD Type 2
** MERGE Logic
***_ Match on natural key + is_current=true
***_ WHEN MATCHED + changed → expire current row
***_ WHEN NOT MATCHED → insert new row
** Two-Step Pattern
***_ Step 1: MERGE to expire old records
***_ Step 2: INSERT new versions for updated records
** Key Columns in MERGE
***_ valid_to = current_timestamp()
***_ is_current = false (expire)
** Alternative
***_ Lakeflow Pipelines AUTO CDC API
***_ Handles out-of-order records automatically
@endmindmap
